storyState.castNotes:
Lin Mo: An ancient book restorer who seems gentle on the surface but actually carries a family mission. You met him at an ancient book auction, and he has a strange protective instinct toward you;
Shen Yan: A mysterious woman claiming to be an information broker. She is a skilled hacker who seems to know the organization's secrets. She trades information with you but her allegiance wavers;
Zhao Qian: A retired special agent, now a cleaner for the mysterious organization. He is hunting you down because you accidentally awakened 'Inkfire'—a sealed textual taboo.
